data.description: Amazing .quiet, suburban retreat with NO HOA on almost 2 acres. This quaint upscale neighborhood with only 8 homes adjoins a beautiful equestrian farm. Enjoy gathering and entertaining in the spacious great room that boasts a dramatic staircase with a wall of windows overlooking a bright and cheerful room.  Nothing is missing in the well designed kitchen, a pleasure to cook in & opens to fireside keeping room - Hardwoods throughout main floor with exception of tile in the kitchen- Luxurious owners suite, which leads to a covered deck, is on the main floor with fireplace and spa like bath with triple shower heads...The walk in custom designed closet is dreamy - Upstairs bedrooms are spacious and there is a loft/bonus area up as well with private exterior entrance - The finished terrace level has a private entrance and is like a home in itself with a bedroom, another spa like bath to enjoy, bar area, media room, HUGE family room, several flex rooms that can be used for anything you desire and walks out to a covered porch - Enjoy relaxing and swimming in the in-ground, salt water pool - Abundant parking includes circular driveway. Other features include built ins throughout, 4 fireplaces, AMAZING coiffured ceilings, wrought iron fence, home generator and  much more - Don't miss your opportunity to own your personal resort!!! MUST SHOW BUYER'S PROOF OF FUNDS OR PRE-APPROVAL PRIOR TO SHOWINGS
